{"type":"message","id":"7f4e79d9","parentId":"a9934d86","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:17:14.157Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 当前 agent 是 **tcm**，也就是这个工作区里的 **“中医助手”**。  \n从当前运行信息看：\n\n- **agent**: `tcm`\n- **名称/身份**: 中医助手\n- **定位**: 中医六经辨证与经方问诊处方辅助 AI\n- **当前渠道**: Feishu\n- **模型**: `openai/gpt-5.4`\n\n如果你想问的是“现在后台到底挂了哪些 agent / session”，我也可以继续帮你查当前会话列表。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0dad2b8d8c4625870169d23699c3608199ba923815962dc16f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":24264,"output":131,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24395,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775384212869,"responseId":"resp_0dad2b8d8c4625870169d236991e348199af340f792fc7ffbd"}}
