{"type":"message","id":"a90eecf7","parentId":"a93f40ab","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:15:11.668Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你好，我在。  \n如果你是要继续看症状，直接把情况发来就行，我会按中医问诊思路帮你整理分析。\n\n最省事的发法：\n\n- 现在最不舒服的是什么\n- 什么时候开始的\n- 怕冷还是怕热\n- 出汗情况\n- 口渴和喝水情况\n- 胃口、恶心、腹胀\n- 大便、小便\n- 睡眠、精神\n- 手脚冷不冷\n- 舌苔、舌质（如果会看）\n\n你也可以直接自由描述，我来替你整理。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_017d928c4c93b0b60169d26e6040f881999c48749a258e19d6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":24959,"output":148,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25107,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775398476482,"responseId":"resp_017d928c4c93b0b60169d26e5f579c8199a94451c33613e2f6"}}
